commit message: Basic support for additional share target for saving a bookmark as read later without going through the ui.
Fix FC on save bookmark to read with no account.
Fix display of unicode characters in about screen webview.
Remove string keys that do not need to be translated from i18n.
Reorganize layouts and change 7' tablet portrait to use phone style single pane ui.
Fix tablet tag list orientation issue and activity titles.
Use search suggest url text for urls.
Add intent to launch app settings from data usage screen.
